<subSubSection lastPageId="10" lastPageNumber="111" pageId="9" pageNumber="110" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="9.[675,1211,1515,1700]" lastBlockId="10.[113,647,216,528]" lastPageId="10" lastPageNumber="111" pageId="9" pageNumber="110">
Au sein du genre 
<taxonomicName authorityName=", Reiche" authorityYear="1841" box="[875,963,1546,1572]" class="Insecta" family="Scarabaeidae" genus="Epilissus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="110" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus" sensu="stricto">
<emphasis box="[875,963,1546,1572]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="110">Epilissus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[972,1005,1546,1573]" pageId="9" pageNumber="110" sensu="stricto">s.s.</taxonomicNameLabel>
redéfini ci-dessus, l’espèce 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Montreuil" authorityYear="2011" baseAuthorityName="Klug" baseAuthorityYear="1833" box="[760,869,1579,1604]" class="Insecta" family="Scarabaeidae" genus="Epilissus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="110" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="prasinus">
<emphasis box="[760,869,1579,1604]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="110">E. prasinus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
semble se rapprocher des espèces du groupe « 
<taxonomicName authority="&quot; (Lebis, 1953)" authorityName="&quot; (Lebis" authorityYear="1953" baseAuthorityName="Lebis" baseAuthorityYear="1953" box="[808,1071,1610,1637]" class="Insecta" family="Scarabaeidae" genus="Arachnodes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="110" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="viridis">
<emphasis box="[808,903,1610,1636]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="110">A. viridis</emphasis>
» (
<bibRefCitation author="LEBIS E." box="[932,1063,1610,1637]" pageId="9" pageNumber="110" pagination="107 - 252" refId="ref13078" refString="LEBIS E. 1953. - Revision des Canthoninae de Madagascar. Memoires de l'Institut scientifique de Madagascar, Serie E. 3: 107 - 252." type="journal article" year="1953">Lebis, 1953</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
, notamment par la présence de fortes crénelures sur la marge interne des métatibias.Ne possédant pas la forte dent sur la marge interne supérieure du paramère droit caractéristique des espèces de ce groupe, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Montreuil" authorityYear="2011" baseAuthorityName="Klug" baseAuthorityYear="1833" box="[535,646,248,273]" class="Insecta" family="Scarabaeidae" genus="Epilissus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="111" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="prasinus">
<emphasis box="[535,646,248,273]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="111">E. prasinus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
pourrait se placer à la base de ce dernier.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="10.[113,647,216,528]" pageId="10" pageNumber="111">
Le maintien de la sous-espèce 
<taxonomicName authority="Lebis, 1953" authorityName="Lebis" authorityYear="1953" class="Insecta" family="Scarabaeidae" genus="Epilissus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="111" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="prasinus" subSpecies="antongilensis">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="111">Epilissus prasinus antongilensis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="LEBIS E." box="[251,378,343,370]" pageId="10" pageNumber="111" pagination="107 - 252" refId="ref13078" refString="LEBIS E. 1953. - Revision des Canthoninae de Madagascar. Memoires de l'Institut scientifique de Madagascar, Serie E. 3: 107 - 252." type="journal article" year="1953">Lebis, 1953</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
ne se justifie pas, aucune différence avancée par l’auteur pour séparer ce taxon de 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Montreuil" authorityYear="2011" baseAuthorityName="Klug" baseAuthorityYear="1833" box="[217,333,407,432]" class="Insecta" family="Scarabaeidae" genus="Epilissus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="111" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="prasinus">
<emphasis box="[217,333,407,432]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="111">E. prasinus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
ne pouvant être retenue. La synonymie entre 
<taxonomicName authority="(Klug, 1833)" authorityName="Montreuil" authorityYear="2011" baseAuthorityName="Klug" baseAuthorityYear="1833" box="[307,646,437,465]" class="Insecta" family="Scarabaeidae" genus="Epilissus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="111" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="prasinus">
<emphasis box="[307,491,437,463]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="111">Epilissus prasinus</emphasis>
(Klug, 1833)
</taxonomicName>
et 
<taxonomicName authority="Lebis, 1953" authorityName="Lebis" authorityYear="1953" box="[142,608,469,496]" class="Insecta" family="Scarabaeidae" genus="Epilissus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="111" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="prasinus" subSpecies="antongilensis">
<emphasis box="[142,468,469,495]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="111">Epilissus prasinus antongilensis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="LEBIS E." box="[477,608,469,496]" pageId="10" pageNumber="111" pagination="107 - 252" refId="ref13078" refString="LEBIS E. 1953. - Revision des Canthoninae de Madagascar. Memoires de l'Institut scientifique de Madagascar, Serie E. 3: 107 - 252." type="journal article" year="1953">Lebis, 1953</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
est donc proposée.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
